{"id":298369,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2013/06/维权网-广西北海白虎头村维权村官许坤出狱/","date":"2013-06-10T08:52:27Z","modified":"2013-06-10T08:52:27Z","title":"维权网 | 广西北海白虎头村“维权村官”许坤出狱，称会坚持维权（图）","content":"<p><div dir=\"ltr\"></p>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" name='more'></a></div>\n<div><span>（维权网信息员梁克专报道）</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">6</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">10</span><span>日上午</span><span>，广西北海市白虎头村“维权村官”许坤刑满出狱。多名村民前往黎塘监狱迎接。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>许坤向本网信息员表示，出狱后会就他被构陷判刑进行申诉，同时他将继续带领村民反抗政府的强征强拆行为。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\">2010</span><span>年</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">5</span><span>月，因为反抗当地政府强征土地，许坤被刑事拘留。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2011</span><span>年</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">8</span><span>月，许坤被以莫须有的“非法经营罪”判处有期徒刑四年，并被处罚金</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">20</span><span>万元。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>许坤哥哥许猛电话：</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">13977925349</span></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\"><br /></span></div>\n<table align=\"center\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\">\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-HXSVQyIRpPE/UbVq0dqRH-I/AAAAAAAAjL8/fXGUeD0cNbY/s1600/73021-1%E8%AE%B8%E5%9D%A4%E5%9C%A8%E9%BB%8E%E5%A1%98%E7%9B%91%E7%8B%B1%E7%AD%89%E5%BE%85%E9%87%8A%E6%94%BE.jpg\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"240\" src=\"http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-HXSVQyIRpPE/UbVq0dqRH-I/AAAAAAAAjL8/fXGUeD0cNbY/s320/73021-1%E8%AE%B8%E5%9D%A4%E5%9C%A8%E9%BB%8E%E5%A1%98%E7%9B%91%E7%8B%B1%E7%AD%89%E5%BE%85%E9%87%8A%E6%94%BE.jpg\" width=\"320\" /></a></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>许坤在黎塘监狱等待释放</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-bHFKrLoTaiU/UbVq1T0e0BI/AAAAAAAAjME/QHM6Hwr5MmA/s1600/73021-2%E8%AE%B8%E5%9D%A4%E7%9A%84%E9%87%8A%E6%94%BE%E8%AF%81%E6%98%8E%E4%B9%A6.jpg\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"320\" src=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-bHFKrLoTai